{"tid":940340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港傳媒唔會講，做 Lasik  原來會引到自殺","createTime":"2018-12-14T00:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T08:25:12.000Z","uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7255c463c7ddf0a192a3f87e10417dae6866405e","tid":940340,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T00:49:51.000Z","msg":"原來好多個案<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n========================<br />\n&bull;Jessica Starr's death was announced by her Fox 2 colleagues on Thursday morning <br />\n&bull;The 35-year-old meteorologist was married and had two young children <br />\n&bull;She was still recovering from Lasik eye surgery when she died <br />\n&bull;In November, she asked fans for their prayers, saying she was finding it 'challenging' getting back to work and her normal life <br />\n&bull;She underwent Lasik eye surgery the previous month after wearing contact lenses for years   <br />\n&bull;It is unclear if the young mother was taking pain medication to help her recover <br />\n&bull;Starr underwent Lasik SMILE surgery which corrects short-sightedness <br />\n&bull;The procedure was approved by the FDA in 2016 and is carried out by doctors across the country <br />\n&bull;It is unclear where Starr underwent her procedure in Detroit <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/13/14/7383528-6492233-image-m-2_1544712674244.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F13%2F14%2F7383528-6492233-image-m-2_1544712674244.jpg&h=c097b4ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n WJBK Fox 2 meteorologist Jessica Starr, 35, took her own life on Wednesday, her colleagues have revealed <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/13/14/7384434-6492233-image-a-25_1544713118433.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F13%2F14%2F7384434-6492233-image-a-25_1544713118433.jpg&h=ed1c43c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Starr's colleagues announced her death tearfully on Thursday morning <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/13/17/7391004-6492233-image-a-17_1544722926072.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F13%2F17%2F7391004-6492233-image-a-17_1544722926072.jpg&h=4a1f330e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Starr shared this image with fans after undergoing Lasik SMILE surgery on her eyes in October <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/13/17/7390976-6492233-image-a-13_1544722751705.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F13%2F17%2F7390976-6492233-image-a-13_1544722751705.jpg&h=dfa4e992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n In a video she uploaded on November 13, Starr said she was having a 'hard go' recovering from the surgery and asked fans on Facebook for their prayers and well wishes<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/13/17/7390974-6492233-image-a-14_1544722775276.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F13%2F17%2F7390974-6492233-image-a-14_1544722775276.jpg&h=e106bca2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n In a video she uploaded on November 13, Starr said she was having a 'hard go' recovering from the surgery and asked fans on Facebook for their prayers and well wishes<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/13/14/7384346-6492233-image-a-12_1544712848601.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F13%2F14%2F7384346-6492233-image-a-12_1544712848601.jpg&h=d75e401e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The day after she posted the video, she revealed that it had been too soon for her to go back to work <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/13/14/7383562-6492233-image-m-4_1544712724285.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F13%2F14%2F7383562-6492233-image-m-4_1544712724285.jpg&h=34fa5e44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Starr and her husband Daniel have two young children. They are shown with their kids, in a photograph she shared with Fox fans on Facebook, and her parents <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/13/17/7383550-6492233-Starr_and_her_husband_Daniel_are_pictured_The_circumstances_surr-m-6_1544722449116.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F13%2F17%2F7383550-6492233-Starr_and_her_husband_Daniel_are_pictured_The_circumstances_surr-m-6_1544722449116.jpg&h=d268ff2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Starr and her husband Daniel are pictured. The circumstances surrounding her death remain unknown <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/13/17/7391068-6492233-image-a-21_1544723040221.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F13%2F17%2F7391068-6492233-image-a-21_1544723040221.jpg&h=d84782f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n In November, Canadian Paul Fitzpatrick, 56, took his own life after blaming the procedure for giving him 20 years of intolerable pain in his eyes.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/12/13/422071897153517892/1024x576_MP4_422071897153517892.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideos.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2018%2F12%2F13%2F422071897153517892%2F1024x576_MP4_422071897153517892.mp4&d=Xm7WKmrItRA9qTfGUjZ%2Fa8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=b2dbf856\" target=\"_blank\">https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/12/13/422071897153517892/1024x576_MP4_422071897153517892.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6492233/Fox-meteorologist-mother-two-35-kills-herself.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-6492233%2FFox-meteorologist-mother-two-35-kills-herself.html&d=Xm7WKmrItRA9qTfGUjZ%2Fa8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=add8332e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6492233/Fox-meteorologist-mother-two-35-kills-herself.html</a>"},{"pid":"baa806d8b1630a54b78ccf187bfb2fe070db1a92","tid":940340,"uid":134226,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T00:53:17.000Z","msg":"dailymail<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b3c0e1ce57de59288f48e63eba1754704c5eb0","tid":940340,"uid":10382,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T00:55:26.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"a047fc17066e8089d236ee55f0bebc6938d30ecd","tid":940340,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T00:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e419aa517e9c5d9b952c53c9cf46f5eae7c01e4","tid":940340,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"baa806d8b1630a54b78ccf187bfb2fe070db1a92","tid":940340,"uid":134226,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T00:53:17.000Z","msg":"dailymail<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:32:48.000Z","msg":"你自己 google &quot;lasik suicide&quot; ，唔係老作，原來有後遺症"},{"pid":"561177c4467a807ccba7e1ffe1b10decb9b3bab7","tid":940340,"uid":61882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8e419aa517e9c5d9b952c53c9cf46f5eae7c01e4","tid":940340,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"baa806d8b1630a54b78ccf187bfb2fe070db1a92","tid":940340,"uid":134226,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T00:53:17.000Z","msg":